    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――長瀬麻奈トリビュートライブ前夜",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅ\n通しで何度歌っても完璧な出来ですわね！",
      "startTime": 7.8883145332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。よし、最後の練習はこれくらいにしておこう",
      "startTime": 11.7549811999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　私はまだ歌えますわ！",
      "startTime": 16.8549811999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈様のトリビュートライブに出演するのですから\nいくら練習しても足りないくらいですわよ！",
      "startTime": 23.6216478665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "前日に無理は禁物だぞ？　俺の目から見ても\n十分に仕上がっているから、安心して休んでくれ",
      "startTime": 30.7883145332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "むぅ……{user}さんがそこまで\n言うなら仕方ありませんわね",
      "startTime": 37.5216478665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "今日はここまでにしておきますわ",
      "startTime": 40.9549811999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いつも頑張ってるけど、今回は特に気合いが入ってるな",
      "startTime": 44.0216478665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "当然ですわ！\n私の歌声がテレビを通じて全国に届くんですのよ？",
      "startTime": 50.4216478665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "下手なパフォーマンスをして\n麻奈様の顔に泥を塗る訳にはいきませんわ！",
      "startTime": 57.4549811999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あまり気負っても良くないぞ……と言いたいところだが\nその顔を見る限り、緊張感もちょうどいいみたいだな",
      "startTime": 66.2883145332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。ライブの後の打ち上げなんだが\nどこにしたい――",
      "startTime": 73.0216478665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "焼肉にしてくださいまし！　これは譲れませんわ！",
      "startTime": 74.1433992703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "はは、分かったよ。俺も候補を考えておくけど\nどこか行きたい店があったら教えてくれ",
      "startTime": 83.6433992703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "分かりましたわ！",
      "startTime": 86.4767326037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ……明日のライブ\n目に物見せて差し上げますわ！",
      "startTime": 91.3816492476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "その使い方はちょっと違うと思うけど……\n楽しみにしてるからな",
      "startTime": 97.7767326037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――トリビュートライブ当日",
      "startTime": 101.010065937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "ぐすっ、私、麻奈様の曲を……\n全国のみなさんに届けることが出来ましたわ……っ",
      "startTime": 110.0767326037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、こんな日が来るなんて……\n本当に、みなさん、ありがとう、ございます……っ",
      "startTime": 120.8433992704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈様、見てくださっていますか……？",
      "startTime": 128.3767326037,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2933.3333332999982,
          "startTime": 131.310065937
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……まったく\nみなさんも本当に麻奈様を愛してらっしゃるのね",
      "startTime": 137.9112579462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、それも当然ですわ！\nだって麻奈様ですもの！",
      "startTime": 145.5433992703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈様、見ていてくださいませ！",
      "startTime": 150.9767326037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "私！　成宮すずは！\n『二代目星降る奇しぇき』と、して……",
      "startTime": 157.7433992703,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_laugh-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5435.057576400027,
          "startTime": 159.9117901801
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5365.858968000026,
          "startTime": 159.8425915717
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "……ここで噛むのはほんとにダメですわーーー！！\n大事なところで何やってるんですの私はーーー！！",
      "startTime": 167.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "ああもう、どうして肝心な時に……え\nもう次の方の出番ですの？",
      "startTime": 177.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5333.333333300005,
          "startTime": 183.2333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5333.333333300005,
          "startTime": 183.2333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clap-03.m4a",
          "delay": 5662.190755199987,
          "startTime": 183.5621907552
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz020.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それではみなさん、ごきげんよ～！",
      "startTime": 180.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――帰り道",
      "startTime": 185.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz021.m4a",
      "text": "Sharing 想像以上の共鳴にFeeling……",
      "startTime": 188.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ご機嫌だな。何を見てるんだ？",
      "startTime": 194.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_01-suz022.m4a",
      "text": "トリビュートライブの感想を検索してましたの\nほら、見てくださいまし！",
      "startTime": 201.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
